    iet determined by ``top``, ``bot`` and ``lengths``.

    EXAMPLES::

        sage: from surface_dynamics.interval_exchanges.integer_iet import cylinder_widths_and_heights

        sage: cylinder_widths_and_heights([0,1],[1,0],[5,2]) == [(1, 7)]
        True
